<p><abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ recipient's copy ]">RC</abbr> (<span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Historical Society of Pennsylvania, Philadelphia ]">PHi</span>). Enclosure missing.</p>
<p><a id="TSJN-01-05-0682-kw-0001" class="keywordref" title="jump to Your excellency's letter of yesterday in text" href="#TSJN-01-05-0682-ks-0001">Your excellencys letter of yesterday</a>: Lafayette probably meant that TJs letter arrived on 24 Apr.; it was, of course, <a href="default.xqy?keys=TSJN-print-01-05-02-0666" class="document">written on 23 Apr.</a></p></div>
